"magical objects, ones that have energy\n" + 
"stored within it that can be released \n" + 
"at will. I've now finished my work on \n" + 
"processing Rainbow Ore, but there is \n" + 
"still much more work to be done.\n" + 
"\n" + 
"@Well, I'm sure there's still plenty\n" + 
"@that we don't know yet. I hope you'll\n" + 
