"@Today I'm interviewing General Eander,\n" + 
"@formerly the highest-ranking officer\n" + 
"@in the Kirgard Royal Army.\n" + 
"@General Eander, not only are you in\n" + 
"@charge of the strongest of the four\n" + 
"@legions, you're also the most \n" + 
"@experienced of all the generals, isn't \n" + 
"@that right?\n" + 
