"@four years ago, and it was the first\n" + 
"@time the capital of Kirgard was under\n" + 
"@threat in over a century. How did that\n" + 
"@happen?\n" + 
"\n" + 
"It was our own fault. We underestimated\n" + 
"them. Never before had the mountain\n" + 
"tribes been a serious threat to us,\n" + 
