"later he'll catch up. If you can't \n" + 
"cripple the enemy early on, you can't\n" + 
"win, and Pereious lacked the capacity to \n" + 
"do that. He hurt our pride, he shook our \n" + 
"foundations, but he did not come even \n" + 
"close to bringing down the kingdom.\n" + 
"\n" + 
"@Still, an impressive feat. Thank you\n" + 
"@for your time, General.\n" + 
