"the world, so I decided to travel to \n" + 
"Mayfall, and then on to Helman Island \n" + 
"and Kirgard, and ask people about the \n" + 
"recent wars between the two countries. \n" + 
"I was hoping to write a book or \n" + 
"something about it. I couldn't believe \n" + 
