$data_interview[42] = 
"@Today I'm interviewing Midian, who\n" + 
"@left the State Army to live as a \n" + 
"@hermit.\n" + 
"@Midian, you used to be a magic \n" + 
"@instructor in the army, right?\n" + 
"\n" + 
"Hmm, a long time ago. I bet you want to \n" + 
"know why I left the army, don't you?\n" + 
"\n" + 
"@I know it was 10 years ago, so it\n" + 
"@coincides with the Triple War between \n" + 
"@Zelmony, Cayeska and the Fairwind \n" + 
"@Republic. Did that have something to\n" + 
"@do with it?\n" + 
"\n" + 
