"just been that it would've been fine.\n" + 
"They -the politicians in Matrech- \n" + 
"crossed the line when they 'subtly'\n" + 
"started to pressure me about my \n" + 
"methods. They didn't just want me to\n" + 
"train them, they wanted me to \n" + 
"indoctrinate them about how wonderful\n" + 
"the State Union is. Oh yes, I knew what \n" + 
"they wanted. It was bloody obvious.\n" + 
"Create a new army in Cayeska loyal to\n" + 
"Zelmony so that after the war they can\n" + 
"fight to join the State Union. I wasn't\n" + 
"having any of that, so they tried to\n" + 
"remove me. That's when I left. I wasn't\n" + 
"going to waste any more of my time on\n" + 
"those idiots.\n" + 
"\n" + 
"@And you'd be living on your own on that\n" + 
"@island ever since?\n" + 
"\n" + 
"Yes, nice and quiet. Away from all that\n" + 
"nonsense. Oh, I don't regret coming \n" + 
"back, but I can't wait to return home \n" + 
"again. I just want to spend my last \n" + 
"days in peace.\n" + 
""

