"steppe and sparsely populated. We're \n" + 
"located on the eastern shores of the \n" + 
"Kubal Sea, an internal sea with the \n" + 
"Kingdom of Issuria to the north, the \n" + 
"Holy Empire of Rocaine to the south, \n" + 
"and the Archduchy of Valcany to the \n" + 
"west.\n" + 
