"Highland that way a while back, and we\n" + 
"got into some trouble with the border\n" + 
"guard there. Wouldn't let us through\n" + 
"without compensation, if you catch my \n" + 
"drift. Long story short, after we got \n" + 
"out of that mess I got in touch with \n" + 
"Rock and decided I'd help him clean up\n" + 
"the place. \n" + 
"\n" + 
