"at the same time, so we served together\n" + 
"for a while, until she got promoted.\n" + 
"I tried talking to her after the whole\n" + 
"mess with Joshua's father, but she \n" + 
"wouldn't listen. I knew from the start\n" + 
"that she had no strong feelings about\n" + 
"Highland. As soon as she got the\n" + 
"opportunity she left to Matrech, and\n" + 
"even as Captain of the Matrech Guard \n" + 
"she didn't ever do a damn thing about \n" + 
"our situation.\n" + 
"\n" + 
"@Well, let's hope things will work out\n" + 
"@now that Highland's getting a fresh\n" + 
"@start.\n" + 
""

