$data_interview[56] = 
"@Today I'm talking to Rorschach, a\n" + 
"@ninja on a quest to avenge his sister.\n" + 
"@So, your sister was a soldier in the\n" + 
"@Kirgard Royal Army, wasn't she? How\n" + 
"@did you end up joining a ninja clan\n" + 
"@instead?\n" + 
"\n" + 
"We were orphans. Joining the army was\n" + 
"the only option we had, but even though\n" + 
"my sister tried to discipline me, I\n" + 
"dropped out after a few weeks. I spent\n" + 
"most of my childhood on the streets, \n" + 
"stealing to survive. Everything changed\n" + 
"when I heard about the Sun clan. Why did\n" + 
"I decide I wanted to join them? I don't\n" + 
"know. My life was meaningless at the \n" + 
