"@of Blackwater and formerly a renowned\n" + 
"@warrior who fought for the State Union.\n" + 
"@Welcome, Shiro. Your name is well-known\n" + 
"@here in Zelmony. You're considered a\n" + 
"@war hero and a legendary warrior, but\n" + 
"@you never actually held a high rank in\n" + 
"@the State Army, did you?\n" + 
